org.apache.spark.sql.api.java.types

Class MapType

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.sql.api.java.types.DataType
      • org.apache.spark.sql.api.java.types.MapType

  • public class MapType
extends DataType
    The data type representing Maps. A MapType object comprises two fields, DataType keyType and DataType valueType. The field of keyType is used to specify the type of keys in the map. The field of valueType is used to specify the type of values in the map.
